  generateName: add-song-to-playlist-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: user_ID
      - name: playlist_ID
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: add-song-to-playlist

          - name: playlist_ID
            value: '{{{{ inputs.parameters.playlist_ID }}}}'

''']
